      "description": "Khaleed accumulates (Desert Power) while moving. After (Desert Power) is fully charged, he will glide on sand, increasing Movement Speed by 35%, making his next Basic Attack deal 50( +140% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to the target (cannot Crit), and reducing the target's Movement Speed by 40% for 1.5s.",
